::Spears::

She ran at full spead and kept running.   She yelled out as she 
ran,"I'll tell Master Prebon you said Hi."  She was getting over 
confident, thinking that she had a good enough lead that they 
coulnd't catch her.  She kept running, hoping to out run them and 
make it back to the trainer base.  She had only gotten about half a 
mile away from the Cybertron Fire, but she wasn't going to let them 
catch her and chop her up.  Then, her maximal program took over.  She 
stopped running and let her body shake.  She looked around and 
wondered how she even got so far from the ship when only a moment 
ago, she was so close to the entrance.  She stood there a moment, 
confused and worried.  She saw Firearm and Lunarpine off in the 
distance.  She took a few steps closer to the base.

Then her trainer program took over.  Her body shook and she turned, 
and started running towards the trainer base.
